i am sorry for any trouble i have caused. My friends told me about the edit feature on this site, and how they screwed up some information; so i decided to see how it worked. I was just seeing how it worked and what i could say. I did not get the first warning message until i had already attempted to change the sites. And I do not believe that i vandalized the general motors information; i just stated what was true. i would like to contribute some information to your site. thank you.

